{"tid":1369986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【攬炒巴入】 有冇美國巴絲打傾下點樣說服美國參眾議員支持香港？","createTime":"2019-07-27T00:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:43:03.000Z","uid":66566,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5762ca145275c9f770f7aa3e311422498fcec5f5","tid":1369986,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:10:22.000Z","msg":"之前攬炒巴發起嘅一人一信俾所屬州／區既參眾議員講香港情況，見到有議員已經開始回覆，支持《美國人權與民主法案》。我認為美國既然係自由世界嘅大佬，佢對香港立場真係好重要。美國既對外政策點行，其他國家大概都會跟住佢點行。<br />\n<br />\n美國政治有一樣嘢叫<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">Lobbying 遊說集團，一般係大公司俾錢俾專業嘅遊說人，利用佢地喺華盛頓嘅人脈關係（Lobbyists一般都係前政府或議會員工），遊說參眾議員佢地喺相關法例既立場上幫到公司嘅利益</span></strong>。例如華爾街嘅大行喺2018選舉年用左近二十億美金既政治經費，最後成功推翻左Obama年代對金融業立嘅某D監管法例。除左大公司，近百個國家如英國、日本都有俾錢俾遊說集團去影響美國嘅外交關係政策去保護佢地國家既利益。可以睇以下既video了解下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MfZB3BrjI74\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMfZB3BrjI74&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=78195b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MfZB3BrjI74</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參議院嘅《美國人權與民主法案》係2016同2017年都有被提出，最後都係被擱置。我希望今次利用遊說集團不斷說服參眾議員，至少帶多一份香港人既聲音入去議會，同時可以長期有人睇住法例嘅進度，匯報俾我地知道DC嘅政治取態同風向，唔好次次都有頭冇尾。因為要由兩院既委員會去到投票立例再俾總統簽埋係需要好多follow up。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人唔係住係東岸，對美國政治其實都冇咩大嘅認識。<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家初步有眾籌請Lobbyists呢個諗法，最先希望遊說兩會嘅Foreign Relations Committee儘快將個法例放上議會討論</span></span>，希望有更熟DC或U.S. Politics ，有文宣／眾籌／管錢／組團／搞活動經驗／英文好嘅巴絲可以一齊傾下。為左保護對話既內容，我會同每人傾一傾然後先add你地入group，都希望攬炒巴團隊如果對呢個idea有咩意見或可以幫助既地方，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可以TG 聯絡我:<span style=\"color: blue;\">offredzzz</span></span>"},{"pid":"1cf15fd8a1c7dd7eeaa7c7a6e88baf3f45eedff5","tid":1369986,"uid":66566,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:12:40.000Z","msg":"More videos on lobbying:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTbtKRdYbYo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaTbtKRdYbYo&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=38756b8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aTbtKRdYbYo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3FYHgfwJnBY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3FYHgfwJnBY&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=5ffe7ad0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3FYHgfwJnBY</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n現時House 既法案係H.R.3289<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/3289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F3289&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=7611d7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/3289</a><br />\n<br />\nSenate既法案係S. 1838. <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F1838&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=426e4b47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1838</a><br />\n<br />\nHow a bill becomes a law<br />\n<a href=\"https://lowenthal.house.gov/legislation/bill-to-law.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowenthal.house.gov%2Flegislation%2Fbill-to-law.htm&d=vhywW4AIbf33TEOu71%2FwUyDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=88ef2748\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lowenthal.house.gov/legislation/bill-to-law.htm</a></span>"},{"pid":"9c72982327284023e5fadde74d4e8b768741d19e","tid":1369986,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4993eb2621d1b05c42406e96faf6b3e734186371","tid":1369986,"uid":143564,"like":0,"d